      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TYPHOON SASKIA (2) has a strong record this track and trip including four wins from five starts. Below best last time at Q Parklands (30.60) in a Grade 5, finishing a 10 length fourth. Rates on top and should go close. SHE'S PEAKIN' (1) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at Q Lakeside over 642m. Yet to miss the placings in eight runs from this box, including three wins. Hard to beat again. TRIPPER ART (6) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Mix 5 at Q Parklands. Can feature with the right run. FIERY WORDS (7) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone.",
